LRZ Server Connection

    • problem: how to install more recent python versions when not using Anaconda (poetry for dependency management)?

Adaptions of Simulation Code

  • 10000 points sampled for testing (1000 before)
  • new noise definition: instead of absolute standard deviation, SNR (signal-to-noise rate) defining the ratio of signal standard deviation to noise standard deviation in the groundtruth; proposed values: 20,10,5
  • HPO: less trials (200, fixed value indepedent of the number of HP of the model - reason: what would be a "fair" solution?)

-> implemented but not used in a simulation yet
